@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qiivzr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(v1))
    v2 = ((tmp + (v1 + 0.72 / v0 + 0.82)) - v1)
    v1 = v0
    tmp = v2
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.40 * tmp + 0.63)) - wp.sin(0.88))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v2 + 0.16) / wp.abs(tmp + 0.82)))
    data[tid] = v0
